WEBVTT

00:00:02.806 --> 00:00:04.442
[NARRATOR] Last
Dragon Ball Z Kai--

00:00:04.509 --> 00:00:06.479
Frieza proved that
he could easily deflect

00:00:06.547 --> 00:00:09.085
even the most powerful
of Vegeta's attacks.

00:00:09.151 --> 00:00:11.356
And as Frieza effortlessly
turned the tables on

00:00:11.422 --> 00:00:13.561
the Saiyan prince,
it seemed the last hope

00:00:13.628 --> 00:00:16.332
of defeating the
tyrant had been lost.

00:00:16.399 --> 00:00:17.068
Until...!

00:00:17.135 --> 00:00:18.671
[GOKU] I'm healed!

00:00:22.211 --> 00:00:25.117
Feels like I can barely keep
my power under control...

00:00:25.184 --> 00:00:28.223
[GOKU] Gohan...!
Krillin...! Piccolo...!

00:00:28.289 --> 00:00:31.797
I'm sorry it took so long,
but I'm coming, right now!

00:00:31.864 --> 00:00:35.003
[NARRATOR] Will Goku arrive
in time to save his friends?

00:00:35.070 --> 00:00:37.341
Find out. Now!

00:00:38.143 --> 00:00:48.363
♪ Opening Song ♪

00:02:13.066 --> 00:02:18.711
[VEGETA struggling]

00:02:18.778 --> 00:02:27.696
[FRIEZA grunting]
[VEGETA struggling]

00:02:27.762 --> 00:02:28.932
Uuugh...

00:02:28.998 --> 00:02:31.402
[cough]

00:02:38.618 --> 00:02:40.454
Da-- Ah, uh...

00:02:40.521 --> 00:02:41.857
[gasp]

00:02:44.630 --> 00:02:46.800
[GOHAN] We can't
just leave him there.

00:02:46.867 --> 00:02:56.853
♪

00:03:24.042 --> 00:03:26.479
[GOKU] Okay...
They're not far off...

00:03:26.546 --> 00:03:28.383
Try to hang on just
a little bit longer!

00:03:28.450 --> 00:03:30.153
I'm on my way, guys!

00:03:30.220 --> 00:03:40.440
[VEGETA painful outcries]

00:03:48.991 --> 00:03:50.861
[GOHAN] Uuuh...

00:03:50.928 --> 00:03:53.501
[VEGETA painful outcries]

00:03:53.567 --> 00:03:55.572
[cough]

00:03:55.839 --> 00:04:00.314
[painful outcries]

00:04:00.381 --> 00:04:03.053
[heavy breathing]

00:04:03.119 --> 00:04:04.689
Hmmm.

00:04:04.756 --> 00:04:12.605
[VEGETA struggling]

00:04:14.876 --> 00:04:16.513
Hm.

00:04:17.181 --> 00:04:20.788
[VEGETA] Aaahhh...!

00:04:44.468 --> 00:04:55.925
[VEGETA painful outcries]

00:04:56.993 --> 00:04:58.329
[FRIEZA] What a shame.

00:04:58.396 --> 00:05:00.968
It seems all the fight
really has gone out of you.

00:05:01.870 --> 00:05:04.308
It's sooner than
I'd have liked...

00:05:04.375 --> 00:05:06.947
[FRIEZA] but I think it's
time to finish you off.

00:05:12.759 --> 00:05:18.871
♪

00:05:18.937 --> 00:05:20.240
[grunt]

00:05:20.307 --> 00:05:30.561
♪

00:05:32.732 --> 00:05:34.067
Hm, hm...

00:05:37.073 --> 00:05:38.610
Hmmm.

00:05:40.915 --> 00:05:45.056
[FRIEZA power yell]

00:05:50.702 --> 00:05:55.143
♪

00:05:55.210 --> 00:05:57.815
[PICCOLO, KRILLIN,
and GOHAN gasp]

00:06:04.629 --> 00:06:06.465
[GOKU] Ah, so I was right.

00:06:06.533 --> 00:06:09.371
That huge power that just
showed up all of a sudden...

00:06:09.438 --> 00:06:12.077
It really was you, huh, Piccolo?

00:06:13.981 --> 00:06:14.949
[PICCOLO] Goku...

00:06:15.016 --> 00:06:16.853
Since you're with
us and not King Kai,

00:06:16.920 --> 00:06:19.392
I'm guessing they brought
you back with the Dragon Balls?

00:06:19.458 --> 00:06:21.428
Ha! Dad! You made it!

00:06:21.495 --> 00:06:24.167
[KRILLIN] So...
you're okay now?

00:06:24.234 --> 00:06:26.172
I'm fine. I feel
better than ever...

00:06:26.239 --> 00:06:27.875
And I owe it all to you guys.

00:06:27.942 --> 00:06:30.915
[chuckles]

00:06:30.982 --> 00:06:32.986
I'm proud of you
for fighting so hard.

00:06:33.053 --> 00:06:35.457
But leave this to me now.
I'll take care of it.

00:06:35.524 --> 00:06:37.127
You'll what?

00:06:37.193 --> 00:06:38.731
Hmmm.

00:06:39.298 --> 00:06:40.601
You can't be
serious, Goku!

00:06:40.668 --> 00:06:42.037
You don't know what
he's capable of.

00:06:42.103 --> 00:06:44.274
And you want us to let you
fight him all by yourself?

00:06:44.341 --> 00:06:45.878
I do.

00:06:47.782 --> 00:06:49.251
Uh...

00:06:49.318 --> 00:06:51.456
Are you sure, Dad?

00:06:51.524 --> 00:06:53.694
This might sound
crazy... but, well...

00:06:53.761 --> 00:06:56.265
you are the real
Goku, aren't you...?

00:06:56.332 --> 00:06:58.303
You're so strong!

00:06:58.369 --> 00:07:00.073
[PICCOLO] Goku, wait!

00:07:01.075 --> 00:07:03.781
[PICCOLO] Krillin's right. He's
become so much more powerful

00:07:03.848 --> 00:07:05.651
than he was on Earth
that it's almost hard to

00:07:05.718 --> 00:07:08.724
believe he's
the same person!

00:07:23.587 --> 00:07:25.524
[GOKU] You must be Frieza...

00:07:25.591 --> 00:07:29.599
Funny, you're a lot smaller
than I thought you'd be.

00:07:30.567 --> 00:07:34.676
Hm. Seems this planet is
positively crawling with scum.

00:07:38.717 --> 00:07:41.556
Vegeta still owes me a rematch.
So if you want him,

00:07:41.623 --> 00:07:43.426
then wait your turn.

00:07:44.394 --> 00:07:47.635
[FRIEZA] I could swear I've
seen him somewhere before...

00:07:47.702 --> 00:07:57.487
[VEGETA struggling]

00:07:57.555 --> 00:08:00.293
About time you came
back, Kakarot...

00:08:00.360 --> 00:08:01.597
Kakarot, eh...?

00:08:01.664 --> 00:08:05.103
Unless I'm mistaken,
that's a Saiyan name...

00:08:08.376 --> 00:08:11.215
[FRIEZA gasp]

00:08:11.282 --> 00:08:12.885
[FRIEZA] It's him!

00:08:13.820 --> 00:08:16.225
[BARDOCK] Frieza...!
Show yourself!

00:08:16.292 --> 00:08:19.232
Come out and
face me, you coward!

00:08:19.298 --> 00:08:22.070
[FRIEZA'S MEN chatter]

00:08:22.137 --> 00:08:23.239
[chuckles]

00:08:23.306 --> 00:08:26.445
Right now...
everything changes.

00:08:26.513 --> 00:08:29.018
[FRIEZA] It's him. It has to be!

00:08:29.085 --> 00:08:31.556
[BARDOCK] It all
comes down to this...

00:08:32.491 --> 00:08:35.564
My fate... Planet Vegeta's...

00:08:36.398 --> 00:08:38.169
Kakarot's...

00:08:39.605 --> 00:08:41.409
And, yes...

00:08:41.475 --> 00:08:44.281
[chuckle] Yours too, Frieza.

00:08:44.348 --> 00:08:51.763
♪

00:08:51.830 --> 00:08:53.332
[BARDOCK] Ahhh!
We settle it here!

00:08:53.399 --> 00:08:55.671
[FRIEZA] He's the spitting
image of that impertinent Saiyan

00:08:55.738 --> 00:08:59.746
who rebelled against me when
I destroyed Planet Vegeta!

00:09:01.215 --> 00:09:02.752
What the--?!

00:09:06.993 --> 00:09:10.133
[laughing]

00:09:10.199 --> 00:09:15.911
[BARDOCK] Aaaahhh...!

00:09:19.552 --> 00:09:23.259
K... Kak-- Kakarot...

00:09:23.326 --> 00:09:27.836
[BARDOCK] Kakarot!

00:09:27.902 --> 00:09:29.471
[FRIEZA] I have no
intention of allowing

00:09:29.539 --> 00:09:32.043
even a single Saiyan to live.

00:09:32.110 --> 00:09:33.379
No point resisting.

00:09:33.446 --> 00:09:37.020
You could save yourself the
trouble and kneel before me now.

00:09:37.087 --> 00:09:38.523
I'm sure I could.

00:09:38.590 --> 00:09:39.893
Huh?

00:09:39.960 --> 00:09:43.733
[VEGETA] He's not the
same person he was before.

00:09:43.800 --> 00:09:46.172
Once again, he's
completely shattered

00:09:46.238 --> 00:09:48.877
his previous limitations...

00:09:49.779 --> 00:09:53.486
[VEGETA] But wait...
Does that mean...?!

00:09:53.553 --> 00:09:56.492
Are you ready, Saiyan?

00:09:56.559 --> 00:09:58.095
Yeah.

00:10:08.950 --> 00:10:10.286
Hm...?

00:10:14.863 --> 00:10:16.900
What happened? Did
Goku do something?

00:10:16.967 --> 00:10:18.369
I barely
saw him move!

00:10:18.436 --> 00:10:19.606
Wow!

00:10:19.672 --> 00:10:21.843
[PICCOLO] Not even
I saw that clearly...

00:10:21.910 --> 00:10:24.815
He's moving even
faster than Frieza!

00:10:26.385 --> 00:10:27.856
Hrmph.

00:10:27.922 --> 00:10:29.391
Mmm...

00:10:37.675 --> 00:10:39.912
Aaah...!

00:10:41.883 --> 00:10:44.387
Watch out, Goku!
Get out of the way!

00:11:02.825 --> 00:11:05.296
[KRILLIN] Goku...! Look out!

00:11:06.465 --> 00:11:08.335
Insolent fool!

00:11:09.705 --> 00:11:11.174
Hyuh!

00:11:12.778 --> 00:11:15.416
[explosion]

00:11:17.320 --> 00:11:18.590
[grunt]

00:11:18.657 --> 00:11:28.877
♪

00:11:35.323 --> 00:11:36.859
Auh!

00:11:36.960 --> 00:11:46.846
♪

00:11:49.317 --> 00:11:50.854
[GOKU] Hya!

00:12:07.788 --> 00:12:10.994
[chuckles]

00:12:13.934 --> 00:12:15.436
[KRILLIN] Eh...

00:12:17.173 --> 00:12:18.843
Uh...!

00:12:31.736 --> 00:12:33.105
That's not... possible.

00:12:33.172 --> 00:12:35.010
There's no way he could
have deflected them all!

00:12:35.076 --> 00:12:37.380
He was only using one hand!

00:12:37.447 --> 00:12:40.320
[chuckling in pain]

00:12:40.386 --> 00:12:41.556
Just a little advice...

00:12:41.622 --> 00:12:43.727
You aren't gonna want to
hold anything back, Frieza...

00:12:43.793 --> 00:12:45.931
Not against this one.

00:12:47.433 --> 00:12:50.240
[VEGETA] You see...
he is what you fear

00:12:50.306 --> 00:12:53.747
more than anything
else in the universe.

00:12:53.813 --> 00:12:55.183
Ughhh!

00:12:55.249 --> 00:12:57.655
You're dealing with
a real Super Saiyan!

00:12:57.721 --> 00:12:58.957
[gasp]

00:12:59.024 --> 00:13:01.228
[VEGETA] Yes, you heard me...

00:13:01.295 --> 00:13:05.871
The legendary warrior;
even mightier than you...!

00:13:05.938 --> 00:13:08.208
He stands before you now!

00:13:08.275 --> 00:13:10.179
[chuckles]

00:13:10.246 --> 00:13:12.084
Just wait... You're
finally about to

00:13:12.150 --> 00:13:13.954
get a taste of true fear...

00:13:14.021 --> 00:13:16.291
one that you've long deserved!

00:13:16.358 --> 00:13:19.598
[laughing]

00:13:22.437 --> 00:13:25.877
[VEGETA] Ahhh!

00:13:29.484 --> 00:13:33.125
[gasping]

00:13:34.427 --> 00:13:36.031
Vegeta!

00:13:37.635 --> 00:13:39.705
Oh, Vegeta...
You forget...

00:13:39.772 --> 00:13:41.208
I don't enjoy jokes

00:13:41.275 --> 00:13:43.580
and you've never
been very funny.

00:13:43.647 --> 00:13:45.918
[gasping]

00:13:45.985 --> 00:13:47.187
Why... you...!

00:13:47.254 --> 00:13:48.790
[GOKU] Vegeta could
barely even move,

00:13:48.857 --> 00:13:50.528
let alone defend himself!

00:13:50.594 --> 00:13:51.863
What you did that's--

00:13:51.929 --> 00:13:54.869
that's nothing short
of cold-blooded murder...

00:13:55.971 --> 00:13:57.608
[FRIEZA] It serves him
right for prattling on

00:13:57.675 --> 00:14:02.050
about that ridiculous
legend. Super Saiyan indeed.

00:14:02.117 --> 00:14:04.989
I do not abide
such foolish talk.

00:14:06.492 --> 00:14:08.028
No!

00:14:08.697 --> 00:14:09.966
[GOKU] Vegeta...

00:14:10.033 --> 00:14:13.172
[VEGETA struggling]

00:14:13.238 --> 00:14:15.376
Ah! Don't tell me
you're still preaching

00:14:15.443 --> 00:14:16.445
that mercy nonsense.

00:14:16.512 --> 00:14:18.684
That means you're
still holding back...!

00:14:18.751 --> 00:14:21.188
You're not really
a Super Saiyan...

00:14:21.255 --> 00:14:22.423
Damn it...

00:14:24.562 --> 00:14:27.033
[GOKU] Krillin, don't do it!

00:14:29.939 --> 00:14:31.175
The only way
you can beat him

00:14:31.241 --> 00:14:32.511
is if you harden your heart!

00:14:32.578 --> 00:14:36.118
You fool! You have to
put aside your mercy.

00:14:36.185 --> 00:14:38.857
Then you might-- might
actually stand a chance.

00:14:38.924 --> 00:14:41.294
You could truly
become a Super Saiyan!

00:14:41.361 --> 00:14:43.667
I don't care what you
say, I could never act

00:14:43.734 --> 00:14:44.969
as cold-blooded as you do.

00:14:45.036 --> 00:14:47.140
Not even if I thought
it'd make me stronger...

00:14:47.207 --> 00:14:48.877
So whatever
this "Super Saiyan"

00:14:48.944 --> 00:14:50.079
thing is you're talking about,

00:14:50.146 --> 00:14:52.016
I think I'll get by just fine.

00:14:52.083 --> 00:14:53.821
A... A Super...

00:14:53.887 --> 00:14:56.893
A Super Saiyan... is what--

00:14:56.960 --> 00:14:58.462
Stop talking.
Save your energy.

00:14:58.530 --> 00:15:01.536
You running your mouth is just
going to make things worse.

00:15:04.407 --> 00:15:05.911
[GOBLIN] Ah!

00:15:05.978 --> 00:15:08.950
[ALL laughing]

00:15:10.955 --> 00:15:12.591
[KING VEGETA] Fire!

00:15:20.975 --> 00:15:24.081
[BOTH chuckling]

00:15:24.148 --> 00:15:30.025
[FRIEZA chuckling]

00:15:31.495 --> 00:15:33.131
[KING VEGETA] Uuuhhh!

00:15:42.818 --> 00:15:43.887
[laughing]

00:15:43.954 --> 00:15:47.060
Well, well!
Now that is beautiful!

00:15:47.127 --> 00:15:49.330
See...? Look, Dodoria! Zarbon!

00:15:49.397 --> 00:15:52.437
Look at the fireworks!
Aren't they splendid?!

00:15:52.505 --> 00:15:55.209
[laughing]

00:15:55.977 --> 00:15:58.917
Please, Kakarot!
You have to listen to me.

00:15:58.984 --> 00:16:00.988
[coughing]

00:16:01.055 --> 00:16:03.994
Is there no way to silence
this blithering buffoon?

00:16:04.061 --> 00:16:06.398
It would seem he's intent
on talking me to death.

00:16:06.465 --> 00:16:09.471
I need you to
know... what happened...

00:16:09.539 --> 00:16:12.812
to Planet Vegeta...
where... we were born...

00:16:12.878 --> 00:16:14.582
It's gone. Destroyed.

00:16:14.648 --> 00:16:16.251
That's true... but not--

00:16:16.318 --> 00:16:19.992
not cause it collided
with a giant meteor.

00:16:20.861 --> 00:16:22.531
[chuckles]

00:16:24.502 --> 00:16:27.975
[VEGETA] It was
Frieza. Frieza did it!

00:16:28.042 --> 00:16:31.114
After we Saiyans
served him faithfully

00:16:31.181 --> 00:16:35.991
a-and blindly followed
his every last order, he...

00:16:36.058 --> 00:16:37.327
he betrayed us.

00:16:37.393 --> 00:16:40.099
He disposed of our
race like common trash,

00:16:40.166 --> 00:16:43.205
wiped us from
existence, so that now

00:16:43.272 --> 00:16:46.211
we are all that remain...

00:16:46.880 --> 00:16:48.817
[VEGETA] They're all gone.

00:16:48.884 --> 00:16:52.256
Your parents.
My father, the king...

00:16:52.323 --> 00:16:54.629
We Saiyans were growing
in strength and numbers,

00:16:54.695 --> 00:16:57.266
and Frieza feared
that soon a Super Saiyan

00:16:57.333 --> 00:16:59.037
would be born among us...

00:16:59.104 --> 00:17:01.676
It terrified him!

00:17:01.743 --> 00:17:04.748
Hm. That old story again?

00:17:04.815 --> 00:17:10.594
[struggling and coughing]

00:17:10.661 --> 00:17:12.932
I... didn't know.

00:17:12.999 --> 00:17:18.009
[VEGETA crying]

00:17:18.075 --> 00:17:20.681
I'm begging you, please!

00:17:20.747 --> 00:17:25.056
Beat him... for me!
For the pride of our race.

00:17:25.122 --> 00:17:27.828
[VEGETA] You must
defeat him... Please...

00:17:27.895 --> 00:17:31.468
He must die by
a Saiyan's hand...

00:17:32.471 --> 00:17:42.490
♪

00:17:46.498 --> 00:17:48.402
[GOKU] Vegeta...

00:17:53.145 --> 00:17:55.884
He's finally finished, is he...?

00:17:55.951 --> 00:18:00.326
Now that he's done, shall
we resume this horror show?

00:18:02.030 --> 00:18:05.136
[GOKU] For you
to actually cry...

00:18:05.203 --> 00:18:07.941
For you to beg me for my help...

00:18:08.910 --> 00:18:12.585
I can only imagine how hard that
must have been for you to do.

00:18:12.652 --> 00:18:20.366
♪

00:18:20.432 --> 00:18:21.268
Hmmmm.

00:18:21.335 --> 00:18:22.872
[YAMCHA] Something
happen on Namek?

00:18:22.939 --> 00:18:25.243
Well, Vegeta...
is dead.

00:18:25.309 --> 00:18:26.679
What? There's no way!

00:18:26.746 --> 00:18:29.552
But... if Vegeta's dead,
then that must mean--!

00:18:29.619 --> 00:18:34.027
Yes, he... Frieza defeated
him... and easily.

00:18:34.093 --> 00:18:36.766
After years of service,
after devoting his

00:18:36.833 --> 00:18:39.438
entire life to Frieza's cause,

00:18:39.505 --> 00:18:41.976
[KING KAI] Vegeta
was betrayed and killed.

00:18:42.043 --> 00:18:44.882
It's a shame,
that's what it is.

00:18:44.949 --> 00:18:48.055
And what a blow
to his Saiyan pride.

00:18:48.122 --> 00:18:49.257
I didn't think there was anyone

00:18:49.324 --> 00:18:51.630
who could defeat
Vegeta... "easily."

00:18:51.696 --> 00:18:53.734
I'm afraid Goku and
the others have stirred

00:18:53.800 --> 00:18:57.106
the anger of a monster
whose fury knows no bounds.

00:18:57.173 --> 00:18:59.111
So what then? Are you
saying that it's hopeless,

00:18:59.177 --> 00:19:01.015
that there's no way
they can ever win?!

00:19:01.081 --> 00:19:03.252
Then... what about Goku?

00:19:03.318 --> 00:19:04.855
He's preparing to fight.

00:19:04.922 --> 00:19:08.095
He's determined to see this
through, no matter the cost.

00:19:08.161 --> 00:19:09.765
Goku!

00:19:11.001 --> 00:19:12.939
But that's insane...

00:19:13.005 --> 00:19:15.844
[KING KAI] Oh, Goku...

00:19:15.911 --> 00:19:25.930
♪

00:19:35.182 --> 00:19:36.786
[GOKU grunt]

00:19:48.475 --> 00:19:50.245
[GOKU] I get it now...

00:19:50.312 --> 00:19:53.754
It wasn't losing your
race that made you so angry.

00:19:53.820 --> 00:19:56.224
At least not entirely.

00:19:56.291 --> 00:19:59.699
You were mad because he
forced you to be his puppet.

00:19:59.766 --> 00:20:02.771
[GOKU] You couldn't
stand losing your pride.

00:20:03.873 --> 00:20:06.645
[ALL shaky breathing]

00:20:08.617 --> 00:20:11.421
I may have hated you
when you were alive...

00:20:14.762 --> 00:20:17.400
But I always
respected your pride.

00:20:17.467 --> 00:20:27.486
♪

00:20:38.108 --> 00:20:42.116
[GOKU] And now... it's time
for me to share that pride.

